@*
    Workload Analysis design system. ONE token family (wa-*) shared by every
    page in the module: Index, Dashboard, Details, Create, Edit, Compare,
    Config. Replaces the patchwork of lt-* / pc-* / wd-* / raw Tailwind
    that the module had grown across seven pages.

    Brand: #005B99 (corporate blue), DGEP 4G excellence aesthetic.
    Design choices:
      - Sticky scenario header on every record-page (Details, Edit, Compare)
        with code pill, name, status, fiscal year, owning unit, actions.
      - One KPI chip pattern reused on Index (filtered totals), Dashboard
        (portfolio totals), Details (single-scenario totals).
      - One card grammar: white card, 1px border, 0.5rem radius, header +
        body, optional foot. Anchor IDs on cards so #fte / #lineitems / etc.
        scroll-and-pulse the right section (matches the sd2-* pattern from
        the Services/Details redesign).
      - One table pattern: sticky thead, striped tbody, dense, 0.78rem
        text. Toolbar above with search + filter + bulk actions.
      - Side panels for complexity/seasonality settings on Edit, replacing
        the four nested Bootstrap modals.
      - Empty-state, status-pill, button, and chart-wrap utilities.

    Drop the partial onto any wa-* page with `<partial name="_WaStyles" />`.
*@
<style>
    /* ============================ LAYOUT ============================ */
    .wa-page { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .75rem; }

    /* Sticky scenario header — used on Details, Edit, Compare. */
    .wa-stickyhead {
        position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 30;
        background: #fff;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        margin: 0 -.75rem .25rem;
        padding: .55rem .75rem .45rem;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(15,23,42,.04);
    }
    .wa-titlerow { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: .75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .wa-titlemain { min-width: 0; flex: 1 1 360px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .wa-code-pill { display: inline-block; padding: .14rem .55rem; font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 700; border-radius: .25rem; background: #eff6ff; color: #1d4ed8; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; letter-spacing: .04em; }
    .wa-title { margin: 0; font-size: var(--fs-base); font-weight: 600; color: #111827; line-height: 1.2; max-width: 480px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; }
    .wa-breadcrumb { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #6b7280; }
    .wa-actions { display: inline-flex; gap: .35rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    /* Page header (used on Index/Dashboard/Config — non-record pages). */
    .wa-pageheader { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: .75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; padding-bottom: .35rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin-bottom: .25rem; }
    .wa-pagetitle { margin: 0; font-size: var(--fs-base); font-weight: 600; color: #111827; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; line-height: 1.2; }
    .wa-pagetitle i { width: 18px; height: 18px; color: #005B99; }
    .wa-pagesub { margin: .15rem 0 0; font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #6b7280; }

    /* ============================ STATUS PILLS ============================ */
    .wa-status-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .25rem; padding: .15rem .55rem; font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 600; border-radius: .25rem; }
    .wa-status-Draft     { background: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b; }
    .wa-status-InReview  { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
    .wa-status-Approved  { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    .wa-status-Archived  { background: #e5e7eb; color: #374151; }

    /* ============================ BUTTONS ============================ */
    .wa-btn { border-radius: .375rem; padding: .35rem .7rem; font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 600; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .35rem; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid transparent; line-height: 1.1; transition: background .12s, color .12s, border-color .12s; }
    .wa-btn-primary { background: #005B99; color: #fff; }
    .wa-btn-primary:hover { background: #003d6b; color: #fff; }
    .wa-btn-outline { background: #fff; color: #005B99; border-color: #cbd5e1; }
    .wa-btn-outline:hover { background: #f1f5f9; color: #005B99; }
    .wa-btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: #374151; border-color: #d1d5db; }
    .wa-btn-ghost:hover { background: #f9fafb; }
    .wa-btn-danger { background: #fff; color: #b91c1c; border-color: #fecaca; }
    .wa-btn-danger:hover { background: #fef2f2; color: #991b1b; }
    .wa-btn-ai { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#a855f7,#6366f1); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(99,102,241,.18); border: none; }
    .wa-btn-ai:hover { color: #fff; opacity: .92; }
    .wa-btn-sm { padding: .25rem .5rem; font-size: var(--fs-xs); }
    .wa-btn[disabled], .wa-btn.disabled { opacity: .5; cursor: not-allowed; }

    /* ============================ KPI STRIP ============================ */
    .wa-kpis { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem; }
    .wa-kpi {
        flex: 1 1 180px; min-width: 180px;
        background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: .5rem;
        padding: .65rem .8rem;
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .65rem;
        text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
        transition: border-color .12s, transform .08s;
    }
    a.wa-kpi:hover { border-color: #93c5fd; transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .wa-kpi-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: .375rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; background: #eff6ff; color: #005B99; }
    .wa-kpi-icon i { width: 16px; height: 16px; }
    .wa-kpi-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-width: 0; line-height: 1.15; flex: 1; }
    .wa-kpi-label { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #64748b; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .04em; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
    .wa-kpi-value { font-size: var(--fs-base); color: #0f172a; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; }
    .wa-kpi-sub   { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #94a3b8; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }

    .wa-kpi.wa-kpi-good .wa-kpi-icon { background: #ecfdf5; color: #047857; }
    .wa-kpi.wa-kpi-warn .wa-kpi-icon { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
    .wa-kpi.wa-kpi-bad  .wa-kpi-icon { background: #fef2f2; color: #b91c1c; }
    .wa-kpi.wa-kpi-good .wa-kpi-value { color: #047857; }
    .wa-kpi.wa-kpi-warn .wa-kpi-value { color: #92400e; }
    .wa-kpi.wa-kpi-bad  .wa-kpi-value { color: #b91c1c; }

    /* Compact KPI strip variant — for the sticky header on record pages. */
    .wa-kpis-inline { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .35rem; margin-top: .4rem; }
    .wa-kpi-chip { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .35rem; padding: .25rem .55rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: .375rem; background: #fafbfc; font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #475569; text-decoration: none; }
    a.wa-kpi-chip:hover { background: #eff6ff; border-color: #93c5fd; color: #1d4ed8; }
    .wa-kpi-chip i { color: #005B99; width: 12px; height: 12px; }
    .wa-kpi-chip b { color: #0f172a; font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--fs-xs); }

    /* ============================ CARDS ============================ */
    .wa-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: .5rem; box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15,23,42,.03); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .wa-card-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: .5rem; padding: .55rem .85rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
    .wa-card-title { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .45rem; font-size: var(--fs-sm); font-weight: 600; color: #111827; min-width: 0; }
    .wa-card-title i { width: 16px; height: 16px; color: #005B99; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .wa-card-count { display: inline-block; min-width: 20px; padding: 0 .4rem; font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 700; line-height: 18px; text-align: center; background: #e2e8f0; color: #334155; border-radius: 9px; margin-inline-start: .35rem; }
    .wa-card-actions { display: inline-flex; gap: .25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .wa-card-body { padding: .85rem; flex: 1 1 auto; }
    .wa-card-body.wa-pad-tight { padding: .45rem .85rem .65rem; }
    .wa-card-foot { padding: .45rem .85rem; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; background: #fafbfc; font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #64748b; }

    /* Anchor highlight pulse — fires on hashchange for #anchor links. */
    .wa-card.wa-pulse { animation: waPulse 1.2s ease-out 1; }
    @@keyframes waPulse {
        0%   { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(0,91,153,.35); }
        50%  { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(0,91,153,.10); }
        100% { box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15,23,42,.03); }
    }

    /* ============================ TABLES ============================ */
    .wa-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
    .wa-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: var(--fs-xs); }
    .wa-table thead th {
        position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1;
        background: #f8fafc; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        padding: .5rem .65rem;
        text-align: start; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;
        font-size: var(--fs-xs); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .03em;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .wa-table thead th[data-sort] { cursor: pointer; user-select: none; }
    .wa-table thead th[data-sort]:hover { background: #eff6ff; color: #005B99; }
    .wa-table thead th[data-sort] .wa-sort-arrow { font-size: var(--fs-xs); opacity: .35; margin-inline-start: .25rem; }
    .wa-table thead th.wa-sort-asc  .wa-sort-arrow,
    .wa-table thead th.wa-sort-desc .wa-sort-arrow { opacity: 1; color: #005B99; }
    .wa-table tbody td { padding: .45rem .65rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; vertical-align: top; color: #1f2937; }
    .wa-table tbody tr:hover { background: #fafbfc; }
    .wa-table tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .wa-table .wa-num { text-align: end; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; }
    .wa-table .wa-mono { font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #1d4ed8; font-weight: 600; }
    /* Numbers must render in LTR even inside an RTL container, otherwise
       signed values like "-17" / "+2,120" come out with the sign rendered
       on the wrong visual side (the minus jumps to the right of the digits
       under bidi neutralisation). Forcing direction + bidi isolation on
       every numeric cell is cheap and only meaningful in RTL mode. */
    .wa-table .wa-num,
    .wa-table .wa-mono,
    .wa-kpi-value,
    .wa-kpi-sub {
        direction: ltr;
        unicode-bidi: isolate;
    }
    html[dir="rtl"] .wa-table .wa-num,
    html[dir="rtl"] .wa-table .wa-mono {
        text-align: end; /* keep numeric cells right-aligned in RTL despite ltr direction */
    }
    .wa-table .wa-row-hot { background: #fef2f2; }   /* gap > 0 */
    .wa-table .wa-row-warm { background: #fef3c7; }   /* gap near zero */

    /* Inline-edit input inside table cells. */
    .wa-table-input {
        width: 100%; padding: .25rem .4rem; font-size: var(--fs-xs);
        border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: .25rem;
        background: transparent; color: #111827;
        font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }
    .wa-table-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: #005B99; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(0,91,153,.12); }
    .wa-table-input.wa-mono { font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; }

    /* Toolbar above tables. */
    .wa-toolbar {
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
        padding: .55rem .85rem;
        background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: .5rem;
        margin-bottom: .55rem;
    }
    .wa-toolbar input.wa-search,
    .wa-toolbar select.wa-filter {
        height: 30px; padding: .25rem .55rem;
        font-size: var(--fs-xs); border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: .25rem;
        background: #fff; color: #111827;
    }
    .wa-toolbar input.wa-search { min-width: 220px; }
    .wa-toolbar input.wa-search:focus,
    .wa-toolbar select.wa-filter:focus { outline: none; border-color: #005B99; box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(0,91,153,.12); }
    .wa-toolbar .wa-toolbar-spacer { flex: 1 1 auto; }

    /* Bulk-actions strip — visible always, greys when empty. */
    .wa-bulk { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem; padding: .35rem .55rem; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: .25rem; font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #64748b; }
    .wa-bulk.wa-bulk-armed { background: #eff6ff; color: #1d4ed8; }
    .wa-bulk.wa-bulk-armed b { color: #005B99; }

    /* ============================ FORMS ============================ */
    .wa-form-grid { display: grid; gap: .6rem; }
    .wa-form-grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .wa-form-grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
    .wa-form-grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .wa-form-grid-2, .wa-form-grid-3, .wa-form-grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    .wa-label { display: block; font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin-bottom: .2rem; }
    .wa-label .wa-req { color: #dc2626; }
    .wa-input, .wa-select, .wa-textarea {
        width: 100%; padding: .42rem .65rem;
        border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: .375rem;
        font-size: var(--fs-sm); background: #fff; color: #111827;
    }
    .wa-input:focus, .wa-select:focus, .wa-textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: #005B99; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0,91,153,.12); }
    .wa-input[readonly] { background: #f8fafc; color: #6b7280; cursor: not-allowed; }
    .wa-help { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #6b7280; margin-top: .15rem; }
    .wa-err  { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #dc2626; margin-top: .15rem; display: block; }

    /* ============================ SIDE PANELS ============================ */
    /* Replaces nested Bootstrap modals on Edit. Slides in from the right. */
    .wa-sidepanel-overlay {
        position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(15,23,42,.35);
        z-index: 1040; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none;
        transition: opacity .18s ease;
    }
    .wa-sidepanel-overlay.is-open { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
    .wa-sidepanel {
        position: fixed; top: 0; bottom: 0; right: 0;
        width: 480px; max-width: 100vw;
        background: #fff; border-inline-start: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        z-index: 1045;
        transform: translateX(100%);
        transition: transform .22s ease;
        display: flex; flex-direction: column;
        box-shadow: -10px 0 30px rgba(15,23,42,.08);
    }
    [dir="rtl"] .wa-sidepanel { left: 0; right: auto; transform: translateX(-100%); }
    .wa-sidepanel.is-open { transform: translateX(0); }
    .wa-sidepanel-head { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: .5rem; }
    .wa-sidepanel-title { font-size: var(--fs-sm); font-weight: 600; color: #111827; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .45rem; }
    .wa-sidepanel-title i { width: 18px; height: 18px; color: #005B99; }
    .wa-sidepanel-body { flex: 1 1 auto; overflow-y: auto; padding: 1rem; }
    .wa-sidepanel-foot { padding: .65rem 1rem; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #fafbfc; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: .35rem; }

    /* ============================ CHARTS ============================ */
    .wa-chart-wrap { position: relative; width: 100%; }
    .wa-chart-wrap.wa-chart-md { height: 260px; }
    .wa-chart-wrap.wa-chart-lg { height: 340px; }

    /* ============================ EMPTY STATES ============================ */
    .wa-empty { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 1.5rem .5rem; text-align: center; }
    .wa-empty-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: .5rem; background: #eef2ff; color: #6366f1; }
    .wa-empty-icon i { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
    .wa-empty-title { font-size: var(--fs-sm); font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin: 0 0 .35rem; }
    .wa-empty-msg { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #6b7280; margin: 0 0 .75rem; max-width: 420px; }

    /* ============================ WIZARD (Edit) ============================ */
    /* Numbered step indicator. Active = brand blue, completed = green checkmark, pending = muted. */
    .wa-wizard-steps { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 .65rem; display: flex; gap: 0; align-items: stretch; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: .5rem; overflow: hidden; }
    .wa-wizard-step { flex: 1 1 0; padding: .65rem .9rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .55rem; cursor: pointer; background: #fff; border-inline-end: 1px solid #f1f5f9; transition: background .12s; min-width: 0; }
    .wa-wizard-step:last-child { border-inline-end: none; }
    .wa-wizard-step:hover { background: #f8fafc; }
    .wa-wizard-step .wa-step-num { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; background: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b; font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .wa-wizard-step .wa-step-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-width: 0; }
    .wa-wizard-step .wa-step-label { font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 600; color: #374151; line-height: 1.2; }
    .wa-wizard-step .wa-step-desc { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.2; }
    .wa-wizard-step.is-active { background: #eff6ff; }
    .wa-wizard-step.is-active .wa-step-num { background: #005B99; color: #fff; }
    .wa-wizard-step.is-active .wa-step-label { color: #1e3a8a; }
    .wa-wizard-step.is-done .wa-step-num { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
    .wa-wizard-step.is-done .wa-step-num::before { content: "\2713"; }
    .wa-wizard-step.is-done .wa-step-num span { display: none; }
    .wa-wizard-content { display: none; }
    .wa-wizard-content.is-active { display: block; }
    .wa-wizard-foot { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: .5rem; padding-top: .65rem; margin-top: .65rem; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }

    /* ============================ FORMULA REVEAL (Config) ============================ */
    .wa-formula {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eff6ff 0%, #fff 100%);
        border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; border-radius: .5rem;
        padding: .75rem .9rem;
        font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #1d4ed8;
    }
    .wa-formula .wa-formula-result { font-size: var(--fs-lg); font-weight: 700; color: #005B99; line-height: 1.1; }
    .wa-formula .wa-formula-expr { display: block; margin-top: .25rem; font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: #6b7280; font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; }

    /* ============================ MOBILE ============================ */
    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .wa-title { white-space: normal; max-width: none; }
        .wa-actions { width: 100%; }
        .wa-actions .wa-btn { flex: 1 1 auto; justify-content: center; }
        .wa-kpi { flex-basis: 100%; }
        .wa-sidepanel { width: 100vw; }
    }
</style>
